# ============================================================
#  v5 lessons list — one chapter per line.
# ============================================================
#
#  FORMAT (full row): grade,lang,subject,chapter
#    grade   = 5..11
#    lang    = uz | ru
#    subject = subject name (fuzzy-matched in Notion)
#    chapter = chapter number (>= 1)
#
#  SHORT FORM: a line with just a chapter number inherits
#    grade/lang/subject from the most recent full row above.
#
#  Lines starting with "#" are comments. Blank lines OK.
#  Trailing "# blah" comments at end of a line are stripped.
#
# ------------------------------------------------------------
#  EXAMPLE — process 5 chapters of one subject + 2 of another:
# ------------------------------------------------------------
#
#   7,uz,jahon tarixi,11
#   12
#   13
#   14
#   15
#   8,uz,fizika,1
#   2
#
# ============================================================
#  EDIT BELOW — delete the example and put your real list.
#  Save and close this file when you're done.
# ============================================================

7,uz,jahon tarixi,11
